Name: Hentball
About the game: 'HentBall' is a 2D brick game consisting of a frame, a playing field and a gradually emerging girl in the background. The goal of the game is to clear the playing field from the blocks that close the girl. Open all the girls and enjoy your victories! 'HentBall' - an exciting game, which presents: -Perfect author's graphics -Resolving background music -Multiple levels with different girls -Procedure generation of blocks.
